==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Matterless
<hw>Mat"ter*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not being, or
having, matter; <as>as, <ex>matterless</ex> spirits</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Davies (Wit's Pilgr.).</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Unimportant; immaterial.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Matter-of-fact</ent>⟦br⟧
